79
00:03:37,540 --> 00:03:41,340
2 Peter 3:8-9

80
00:03:41,340 --> 00:03:42,940
「親愛的弟兄

81
00:03:42,940 --> 00:03:45,540
有一件事你們不可忘記

82
00:03:45,540 --> 00:03:48,340
就是主漢一日如千年

83
00:03:48,340 --> 00:03:49,940
千年如一日

84
00:03:49,940 --> 00:03:52,740
主所應許的尚未成就

85
00:03:52,740 --> 00:03:55,140
有人以為他是擔言

86
00:03:55,140 --> 00:03:56,740
其實不是擔言

87
00:03:56,740 --> 00:03:58,640
乃是寬容你們

88
00:03:58,640 --> 00:04:00,740
不願有一人沉淪

89
00:04:00,740 --> 00:04:02,740
乃願人人都悔改」

90
00:04:02,740 --> 00:04:04,540
Now, dear friends,

91
00:04:04,540 --> 00:04:08,740
do not let this one thing escape your notice

92
00:04:08,740 --> 00:04:13,840
that a single day is like a thousand years with the Lord

93
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:17,340
and a thousand years are like a single day

94
00:04:17,340 --> 00:04:22,040
The Lord is not slow concerning his promise

95
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:24,340
